## Description {#details}

An interval data composed by a <em>Left</em> and <em>Right</em> points and an associated <em><a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/value">Value</a></em>.

<em>PointT</em> corresponds to the interval endpoints type. <em>ValueT</em> corresponds to the interval value type.

Definition at line 198 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/adt/intervaltree-h">IntervalTree.h</a>.
